    "name": "Geomancer",
    "description": "You know how to draw power from the land around you, no matter the terrain, by attuning your magic to match its mystical properties.\nYou might be a druid with an elemental focus (such as the flame, stone, or wave orders) or a naturalist with a touch of magic at your disposal. You could concentrate on a single type of terrain to wring every last drop of power from it or choose to wander the land to experience every type of terrain possible.",
